headline: Teamsters launch Massachusetts strike over Republic Services contract
summary: Teamsters Local 25 represents about 450 workers that service over a dozen municipal contracts. The union has threatened to extend the strike to other parts of the country if the two sides cannot come to terms.

headline: REPUBLIC SERVICES TEAMSTERS LAUNCH STRIKE
summary: This morning, 450 Republic Services workers represented by Teamsters Local 25 were forced on strike by the waste giant, inevitably disrupting waste collections for hundreds of thousands of residents throughout the Boston area. Primary picket lines could extend nationwide and result in a work stoppage for over 3,500 Teamsters.
